    "description": "An unlocated ancient city mentioned by Ptolemy and placed by him on the Psathis river, which is also unlocated. BAtlDir tentatively suggests Auchis may have been located in the area of modern Taman’ i.e. at the west end of the ancient Hermonassa island in the Kerch Strait.",
